This book illustrates dozens of bank buildings. They are divided into three parts: Building shape, Public space, and VIP space.

Architecture projects have magnificent presentations in form shaping, facade management, detailing, etc.

Interior projects replaced obsolete design with fresh modern styles. Various design elements are used to highlight individualities of modern banks.
